      <procstep>
        <procdesc>Dataset copied from the cd obtained from Washington, DC 2005

DC GIS staff acquired the district property list from OPM.  Since the database contained square, suffix, and lot values and the addresses were not complete for some records, staff geocoded the records using SSL on the property database.  Those that could not match on SSL were researched and placed using property maps, planimetrics, and the 2005 orthophoto.  Four records could not be placed.</procdesc>
